<emphasis id="F689EA98B629CD4159CBF93AFE82A2AA" bold="true" box="[226,375,1754,1771]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">MEASUREMENTS</emphasis>
</emphasis>
<emphasis id="F689EA98B629CD4158A8F933FE7FA2AF" bold="true" box="[385,394,1747,1774]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">(</emphasis>
<emphasis id="F689EA98B629CD4158A2F93BFE45A2AA" bold="true" box="[395,432,1755,1771]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">
<subScript id="587934CFB629CD4158A2F93BFE45A2AA" attach="right" box="[395,432,1755,1771]" fontSize="7" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">MM</subScript>
</emphasis>
<emphasis id="F689EA98B629CD415899F933FE35A2AF" bold="true" box="[432,448,1747,1774]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">).</emphasis>
N = five males, mean (range). Length of body: 17.34 (16.05–17.95); length of fore wing: 22.09 (19.40–23.35); width of fore wing: 8.30 (7.50–8.60); length of head: 3.29 (3.05–3.45); width of head including eyes: 6.21 (5.95–6.65); width of pronotum including suprahumeral plates: 7.27 (6.95–7.55); width of mesonotum: 5.90 (5.55–6.20).
</paragraph>
